name.description:
Finish setting up your SmartIR device.

For MQTT and UFO-R11 (Moes/Tuya ZS06) IR blasters via Zigbee2MQTT, enter the `/set` topic such as `zigbee2mqtt/ufo_r11/set`. For Tuya blasters, enter a `remote.*` entity id, or a JSON config with mode `cloud` (needs `remote_id`) or mode `localtuya` (needs `entity_id` and `dp`). For Infrared, choose an existing Home Assistant `infrared.*` emitter entity.

Test status: {status}
